    "Legal professionals in urban centers benefit from advanced tools, but those in rural areas often encounter infrastructure gaps and limited training.",
    "Similarly, public users with low digital literacy struggle to navigate digital legal services, even when such services are accessible.",
    "Capturing their perspectives through interviews and focus groups would provide a more balanced view of the current landscape and potential barriers to scalability.",
